## Webhook Event Reference

### Push Event

| Field | Path in payload | Example |
|-------|----------------|---------|
| Repository | `payload.repository.full_name` | `"octocat/hello-world"` |
| Branch | `payload.ref` (strip `refs/heads/`) | `"refs/heads/main"` -> `"main"` |
| Commit SHA | `payload.after` | `"a1b2c3d4e5f6..."` |
| Deletion | `payload.after === "000...000"` | Branch was deleted |
| Installation | `payload.installation.id` | `12345678` |
| Sender | `payload.sender.login` | `"octocat"` |

### Pull Request Event

| Field | Path in payload | Example |
|-------|----------------|---------|
| Action | `payload.action` | `"opened"`, `"synchronize"`, `"closed"` |
| PR Number | `payload.pull_request.number` | `42` |
| Head SHA | `payload.pull_request.head.sha` | `"a1b2c3d4..."` |
| Head Ref | `payload.pull_request.head.ref` | `"feature-branch"` |
| Base Ref | `payload.pull_request.base.ref` | `"main"` |
| Merged | `payload.pull_request.merged` | `true` / `false` |
| Repository | `payload.repository.full_name` | `"octocat/hello-world"` |

### Installation Event

| Field | Path in payload | Example |
|-------|----------------|---------|
| Action | `payload.action` | `"created"`, `"deleted"` |
| Installation ID | `payload.installation.id` | `12345678` |
| Account Login | `payload.installation.account.login` | `"octocat"` |
| Account Type | `payload.installation.account.type` | `"User"` or `"Organization"` |

